title.narrative: Secretary-General support and consultation with Member States, Commonwealth organisations and others

description.narrative:
The main aim of this project is to support the effective representational and leadership role of the Secretary-General in the wider Commonwealth and global communities; to ensure that the Commonwealth values and networks are vibrant and sustained.
The Secretary-General is the main enabler; negotiator and the convenor of the Commonwealth. Therefore, the project encompasses all aspects of the operations of the Office of the Secretary-General in order to support the SG to ensure that she delivers to the satisfaction of the its members.
